# Blog Post Styling Guidelines

When modifying blog post templates in `templates/blog/*/*.html`:

- **Utilize existing stylesheets** - Don't create custom inline styles or new CSS files
- **Maintain consistency** - Follow the patterns and structure used in other blog posts
- **Preserve template structure** - Keep the metadata blocks (meta_description, meta_title, etc.) intact
- **Reference existing posts** - Look at other posts in the same category for styling patterns
